{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.get()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/get","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><em><code>get()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>O método get() da interface <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> retorna o primeiro valor associado com a chave fornecida de um objeto do tipo FormData.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Nota</strong>: Este método está disponível em <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nome<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append_parameters","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"nome\"><code>nome</code></dt>\n <dd>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> representando o nome da chave que queira retornar.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retorno","title":"Retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormDataEntryValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> contendo o valor.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A linha abaixo cria um objeto vazio do tipo FormData.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Se adicionarmos dois valores usuario_nome usando <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>FormData.append</code></a>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'usuario_nome'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Sabrina'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'usuario_nome'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Antônio'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A função get() abaixo apenas irá retornar o primeiro valor usuario_nome incluido:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'usuario_nome'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Retorna \"Sabrina\"</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-get\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'get()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Released on 2015-06-30.\">39.0</a> (39.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"co