/td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\" title=\"Using XMLHttpRequest\">Using XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\" title=\"DOM/XMLHttpRequest/FormData/Using_FormData_objects\">Using FormData objects</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método get() da interface FormData retorna o primeiro valor associado com a chave fornecida de um objeto do tipo FormData.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"FormData.get()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"